{"tid":1492092,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"攬炒警告","createTime":"2019-08-20T16:22:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T16:57:27.000Z","uid":264480,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ce9f2d234fc8ec2f6a44084aac64a0664f224895","tid":1492092,"uid":264480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T16:22:59.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">攬炒警告</div><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">此乃香港人對特區政府及中聯辦的最後通牒，特區政府必須於8月31日之前答應五大訴求，並重組警隊，否則香港人將否定特區政府及中聯辦之合法性，並於9月28日或之前成立臨時政府及臨時立法會。</span>"},{"pid":"8024d28fb4c714b59329e51b9071ed2096ca71c9","tid":1492092,"uid":264480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T16:24:42.000Z","msg":"Push！！！"},{"pid":"d10a0133c1bc55c52f6e49e0ea306f8a9b92a1a8","tid":1492092,"uid":264480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T16:27:53.000Z","msg":"其實最後仲有一句：並宣佈獨立。"},{"pid":"53f24571ac6bf65287bd2a80a8c8fbb8a95e28d4","tid":1492092,"uid":264480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T16:30:42.000Z","msg":"Push!!!"},{"pid":"efac00f366e42c0341373b19dd922dbe02a56962","tid":1492092,"uid":2562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T16:32:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PXcMrux.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPXcMrux.jpg&h=54112853&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PN4V4gd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPN4V4gd.jpg&h=bf41982c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/20/233941_35db8952adc66a9b8fad2b475503a348.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F20%2F233941_35db8952adc66a9b8fad2b475503a348.jpeg&h=ba2d15e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0y2D12U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0y2D12U.jpg&h=c7bab806&